NUCC Health Care Provider Taxonomy code set
-------------------------------------------

© American Medical Association on behalf of the National Uniform Claim
Committee (NUCC).

This product bundles the NUCC Health Care Provider Taxonomy code set (under
src/services/taxonomy/data/) for offline specialty resolution. The code set is
developed and maintained by the National Uniform Claim Committee (NUCC) and is
used and redistributed here under the NUCC permission, which grants a
royalty-free, non-exclusive right to incorporate and redistribute the code set
on the condition that this AMA copyright notice accompanies any copy and the
code set is not modified beyond formatting.

The bundled code set is redistributed unmodified beyond formatting: the build
script (scripts/generate-taxonomy-data.ts) drops the upstream Notes column,
trims field whitespace, sorts rows by code, and re-encodes the data as a typed
TypeScript module. No code, description, classification, or other data value is
altered.

